import { Component, OnInit, AfterViewInit } from '@angular/core'; import { trigger, query, stagger, animate, style, transition } from '@angular/animations' import { AnalyticsService } from 'src/app/services/analytics/analytics.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-footer', templateUrl: './footer.component.html', styleUrls: ['./footer.component.scss'], animations:[ trigger("animateFooter", [ transition(":enter", [ query("*", [ style({opacity: 0, transform: "translateY(100%)"}), stagger(50, [ animate( "250ms cubic-bezier(0.35, 0, 0.25, 1)", style({opacity:1, transform: "none"}) ) ]) ]) ]) ]) ] }) export class FooterComponent implements OnInit { constructor( public analyticsService: AnalyticsService ) { } ngOnInit(): void { } }
